messages.content: Hello, I want to see more things made out of bee hides!

Bee hides, as in the material from bees, isn't a thing. Bees have exoskeletons made of chitin, not hides or skin like mammals. If you're thinking of something creative or conceptual using bee-like patterns or textures, perhaps consider materials that mimic the look of bee exoskeletons or artwork inspired by bees. This could include fabrics, sculptures, or other mediums artistically rendered to evoke the essence of bees, rather than using actual bee parts.
ok, can we pretend? and make some pictures of people in their houses with bee hide trophies?
